# VS Code per-machine settings.
# The ESP-IDF extension writes machine-specific values into .vscode/settings.json
# (idf.currentSetup, idf.port, absolute toolchain/clangd paths). Those must not be
# committed - they break other contributors' machines. Keep them local instead.
# Portable, project-level VS Code config lives in workspace.code-workspace and
# .vscode/extensions.json, which ARE tracked.
**/.vscode/settings.json
